      <title>佩尔茨得到 ISS 的支持，商界领袖参与迪士尼之战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/peltz-backed-to-improve-disney-by-group-of-business-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳尔逊·佩尔茨 (Nelson Peltz) 在加入娱乐公司华特迪士尼公司 (Walt Disney Co.) 董事会的过程中得到了一家有影响力的股东咨询公司和一群商界领袖的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/peltz-backed-to-improve-disney-by-group-of-business-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 12:59:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通称英国财政部可能会加速退出国民西敏寺银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/uk-treasury-s-natwest-exit-may-be-sped-up-jpmorgan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[NatWest Group Plc 要求股东批准一项计划，只要监管机构按计划简化英国上市规则，该计划将使其能够更快地从英国政府回购股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/uk-treasury-s-natwest-exit-may-be-sped-up-jpmorgan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 12:52:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉能可暂时停止澳大利亚矿山开采，锌价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/copper-resumes-rally-as-fed-rate-signals-boost-industrial-metals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉能可公司 (Glencore Plc) 位于澳大利亚北部的麦克阿瑟河 (McArthur River) 锌铅矿因飓风而暂时停止运营，随后锌价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/copper-resumes-rally-as-fed-rate-signals-boost-industrial-metals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 02:19:03 GMT</pubDate>
